## Validation by change type

### Small bugfix

- Run the most specific regression test.
- Run relevant static checks if available.
- Explain why broader validation was or was not needed.

### Feature slice

- Run targeted tests.
- Run static checks/build.
- Run related integration tests if behavior crosses boundaries.

### Refactor

- Prove behavior did not change.
- Run existing tests for the affected area.
- Run build/typecheck/lint where available.

### High-risk change

- Require explicit authorization.
- Run full relevant validation.
- Include rollback notes.
- Consider human approval.

